  | MY PERSONAL I.C.T. LIBRARY |
  +----------------------------+
         (... for now...)

This is the list of the books I've bought till now and that I
use to practice with program development...

Some of them are written in English, the others in Italian.

- Gamma, Helm, Johnson, Vlissides ("Gang of Four") - Design
  Patterns (Addison Wesley);

- Arnold, Gosling, Holmes - JAVA Manuale ufficiale SECONDA
  EDIZIONE ITALIANA (Addison Wesley);

- Fowler - UML DISTILLED Guida rapida al linguaggio di
  modellazione standard (PEARSON Addison Wesley);

- Principe - Java 7 GUIDA COMPLETA (APOGEO);

- Odom - Le Reti Nozioni di base (Cisco Press);

- Ferguson, Schneier, Kohno - Il manuale della crittografia
  (APOGEO);

- Freeman, Freeman - Head First Design Patterns (O'REILLY);

- Sierra, Bates - Head First Java (O'REILLY);

- Anderson, Benedetti - Head First Networking (O'REILLY);

- Malik - Java Programming: From Problem Analysis to Program
  Design (COURSE TECHNOLOGY CENGAGE Learning);

- Comi - Java 7 (APOGEO Pocket);

- Valade - PHP & MySQL FOR DUMMIES (Wiley Publishing).

